<h1>Track Your Workout and Stay Healthy!</h1>

<p>The workout page enables users to effortlessly log their physical activity, including exercise type, duration, intensity level, and calories burned, with the app calculating the total calories burned for the day, providing a comprehensive way to monitor progress towards fitness goals and stay motivated towards achieving them.</p>



<h2>How does the Workout feature work?</h2>
 <ul>
<li>Open the workout page on the app or website.</li>
<li>Select the type of workout from the drop-down menu. Options include bicycling, running, walking, swimming, skiing, climbing, or strength/weight training.</li>
<li>Choose the intensity level of your workout. You can select from easy, moderate, or vigorous.</li>
<li>Enter the duration of your workout, including the start and end times.</li>
<li>Input the number of calories burned during your workout.</li>
<li>Click "Save" or "Submit" to log your workout.</li>
<li>Check the bottom of the page to see the total calories burned for the day.</li>
</ul>


<p>To get started with the User Weights feature, simply log in to your account and navigate to the User Weights page.</p>